Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将来一定会是个好妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有心上人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没...没有啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淑乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牧场的工作已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我送饭团到纱奈那儿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那边的人手一定不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢哪一种女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要胸部大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么问这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说没事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我嘛 很重耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 这点痛忍一忍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很痛嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 是小春和新十郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羙怜？你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么行不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱奈早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭团带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回道场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我向淑乃问好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啦 等等我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了那一晚的大火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算慢慢恢复了平静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在那场大火之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御影那些家伙就不见踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只说有要紧的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你马上进城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备好就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将...将军大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请...请恕属下失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽...丽琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我突然不告而别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我只能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有件事我非查清楚不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指神秘之剑“已鎚”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇见御影了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳 你究竟是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来得跟你说清楚才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自古就流传着“魔剑”的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是从中国流传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻没人相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到信长大人攻陷高野山为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 魔剑就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是“已鎚”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来信长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借着“已鎚”的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出兵中国 但卻输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大陆有把剑能与“已鎚”对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就是圣剑“光轮”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳就是守护“光轮”一族的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽琳 你...？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后传至丰臣家的“已鎚”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在丰臣秀吉死后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成了德川的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是丰臣家的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻意图夺回“已鎚”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷将许多间谍送进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是家康大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将魔剑“已鎚”分成刀身与刀柄两部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始肃清知道这个秘密的丰臣家后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就在一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自上方的少女出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我丰臣家的余党
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在找寻“已鎚”的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令铁舟斋带着我的亲笔信前往中国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望在“已鎚”复活之时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国能将“光轮”借给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要派家父去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他原本就是柳生家的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然因故离开了柳生家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻仍然是我的左右手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到一个月前的某个晚上...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被偷了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了掩人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋因而踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那御影他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御影真幌...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母被德川杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨德川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且发誓一定要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家族代代都会读心术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那个时候 我触碰到你的内心世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心在摇晃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来治疗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想变成什么样的武士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了不起剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋 纳命来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎 你居然故意...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我精硏剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却死在剑下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死在你的剑下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我害怕跟你刀剑相向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样终于解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不让这种事再发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找到新的剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出能夠救人的剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么放不下心的话 就现在和他打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和他光明正大的较量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟自己分个高低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他涉世未深
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者应该说我懂的太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想打赢他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好确认自己的命运如何罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我退出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经帮不上忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修平寺就在今天解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开“已鎚”封印后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾将打败幕府
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还並不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前 希望与楯冈新十郎一决勝负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾将在秋分前后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造访江户城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望阁下在此之前能将圣剑拿到手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立书者　御影真幌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是所谓的挑战书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们德川家咎由自取
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不希望因而再度发生战乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 可以请你接受挑战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果家父来不及...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太自私了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要替幕府比赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛为了那种无聊的比剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的命赔进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你怎么可能赢得过他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也看过他的本事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去啦 新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎第一次想要比赛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是淑乃...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替他想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎也是位剑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然决定了 那么从明天开始就得练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对...对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个送你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护身符？你怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在神签非常灵验的神社买的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那位女巫真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白晰无瑕的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大大的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随风飘逸的盆发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种就是所谓的妖艳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来...该不会...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 那间神社在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很想再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔由罗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定接受挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来告诉你这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还能再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能多和你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为...为什么...？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果铁舟斋大人还是没赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎会怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看他那样 他可是很固执的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还活着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪一郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人怀念的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后 在九州拜师学艺的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开江户 来到了上方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇见了藏身山中的丰臣余党
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同行尸走肉般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便在那个村子住了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了与你並驾齐驱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而专心致力于研习剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 在两年前的某一天...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家时发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村人全被幕府那些家伙杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后与幸存者一起行动的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才知道你受雇于幕府...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丰臣与德川之间的争战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我並不赞同这场争战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所追求的“活人”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否真能拯救世人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒要确认看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道现在不应该打扰你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是有件事我非问你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神社那个人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是修平寺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她要亲你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却体会到在这世上存在着各式各样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她觉得很悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只把御影当成坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实每个人都背负着某些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连胸部也会变大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁舟斋大人他...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说在等人 还在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎 这是圣剑“光轮”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快离开这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好打喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逞强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把就是圣剑“光轮”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要和我打？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想跟你打
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为跟德川那些腐败武士打
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点意义也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是圣剑...“光轮”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也开始吧 铁舟斋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好...好...好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎他...没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“光轮”会保护他的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就得靠他自己了...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御影 我们换地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:23:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静下来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在上面...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天修阁上面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.34,0:24:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新十郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.60,0:24:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱上他之后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.34,0:25:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的观点改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.04,0:25:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有点烦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.12,0:26:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情有着些微变化
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.42,0:26:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为总是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以早已习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.36,0:26:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯他的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投注在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.74,0:26:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.82,0:26:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜欢什么样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.86,0:26:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽无法尽情对他撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心卻仍沸腾不止
